author: Inside Edition
description: More information has emerged about the horrific murders of Rob Reiner and his wife, Michele, and the shocking arrest of their son, Nick, on murder charges. Their daughter, Romy, reportedly discovered her parents' bodies inside their estate. According to a published report, the Reiners "throats were slit." Rob and Michele reportedly had a loud argument with Nick at Conan O'Brien's Christmas party on Saturday night.
title: Rob And Michele Reiner's Son Nick Accused Of Killing His Parents

author: Inside Edition
description: Authorities believed they had a person of interest in the Brown University shootings and detained a 24-year-old former US Army sniper at a hotel 20 miles from the Ivy League campus. But less than 24 hours later, police found that basic forensic tests showed they had the wrong person. John Miller, CNN's chief law enforcement analyst, claims there is a turf war between federal and local Rhode Island cops. More students are speaking out about the hours of terror.
title: Chaos As Hunt For Brown University Shooter Continues

author: Inside Edition
description: Last week, Doordash driver Kourtney Stevenson was seen in a doorbell video appearing to spray something on the bag she was delivering. Homeowner Marc Cardin says his wife, Mandy, felt sick after eating the food at their home in Indiana. Police arrested Stevenson, and she has been charged with consumer product tampering and battery. Stevenson told authorities she was spraying a spider, not the food. The local sheriff isn't buying it.
title: Doordash Driver Charged For Allegedly Pepper Spraying Food

author: Inside Edition
description: AAA says 122 million travelers are expected to hit the roads and skies. Inside Edition's Steven Fabian got some hacks to help make your trip a little easier. Former flight attendant and etiquette expert Elaine Swann says you can have your loved ones follow along on your trip by sending them a text to help you stay connected as you travel. If you are worried about the amount of liquid you are flying with you have options, like finding solid forms of shampoo and conditioner.
title: Hacks To Help Make Holiday Travel Easier

author: Inside Edition
description: Tributes are pouring in for Rob Reiner. Jerry O'Connell, who starred in Reiner's 1986 coming of age film "Stand By Me" when he was 11, says Reiner was like a father to him. Kathy Bates, who Reiner directed in "Misery," told Inside Edition, "I'm horrified. Absolutely devastated. I loved Rob. He was brilliant and kind. He changed the course of my life." President Donald Trump struck a different tone on Truth Social about the slaying of Reiner, who was known for his progressive left-wing politics.
title: Tributes Pour In For Director Rob Reiner

author: Inside Edition
description: Taj tells Inside Edition Digital’s Deborah Hastings why he is retelling his improbable journey, and why it should matter to others.
title: How Taj Rowland Was Kidnapped, Sold, Then Adopted #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: Actor and director Rob Reiner has died. He and his wife, Michelle Singer Reiner, were reportedly found stabbed to death in their home on Sunday. The LAPD is investigating what it's calling an apparent homicide at the residence. SAG-AFTRA confirmed their deaths with a statement honoring the life and work of the prolific filmmaker. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Rob Reiner And Wife, Michelle, Stabbed To Death In Their LA Home
